{"word":"ῥοθέω","slug":"ῥοθέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n92635\" key=\"r(oqe/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ῥοθ-έω</orth>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ῥόθος</etym>) <sense id=\"n92635.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">make a rushing noise</tr_>: hence, of a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">roaring</tr_> fire, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐν ῥοθοῦντι κριβάνῳ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg008:309\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">309</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n92635.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of any confused <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">noise</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ταῦτα . . ἐρρόθουν ἐμοί</foreign> such <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">clamours they raised</tr_> against me, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg002.perseus-grc1:290\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ant.\">Ant.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">290</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λόγοι . . ἐρρόθουν κακοί</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">there was a noise of</tr_> angry words, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg002.perseus-grc1:259\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">259</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}